[URA-ACCA] Like his
relationship with Koito Nagase.

00:20:19.552 --> 00:20:22.597 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] And his relationship
with Ai's mother.

00:20:23.848 --> 00:20:27.352 position:50% align:center
[TAE]
Please just listen to us.

00:20:27.435 --> 00:20:31.898 position:50% align:center
We've been thinking that
we might like to start dating.

00:20:34.317 --> 00:20:36.194 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE] Wait, you mean
that crazy theory?

00:20:36.277 --> 00:20:39.572 position:50% align:center
That my uncle might have been
wrapped up in Koito's suicide?

00:20:39.656 --> 00:20:41.533 position:50% align:center
I told you, there's no way.

00:20:41.616 --> 00:20:42.909 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Annoying.

00:20:42.992 --> 00:20:44.786 position:50% align:center
I guess we'll never
find out the truth about Koito

00:20:44.869 --> 00:20:46.538 position:50% align:center
unless we bring her back
and ask her ourselves.

00:20:46.621 --> 00:20:48.540 position:50% align:center
[STUDENT D]
See ya, Mister S!

00:20:48.623 --> 00:20:50.792 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Have a good one!

00:20:50.875 --> 00:20:52.627 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU] As in there might
be a complicating factor

00:20:52.711 --> 00:20:55.213 position:50% align:center
we've yet to consider.

00:20:55.296 --> 00:20:58.508 position:50% align:center
Ai likes Mister Sawaki, too.

00:20:58.591 --> 00:21:00.552 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA] If the truth
were an easy thing to find,

00:21:00.635 --> 00:21:03.263 position:50% align:center
then no one would
ever struggle or grow.

00:21:03.346 --> 00:21:06.433 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] The human heart
is difficult to fathom.

00:21:06.516 --> 00:21:07.976 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA] It looks like
Ai's made up her mind

00:21:08.059 --> 00:21:10.061 position:50% align:center
to hunt down the truth,

00:21:10.145 --> 00:21:13.857 position:50% align:center
but we'll have to see
where that leads her.

00:21:13.940 --> 00:21:15.525 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I--!

00:21:21.531 --> 00:21:23.366 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I'm...

00:21:26.911 --> 00:21:29.622 position:50% align:center
I'm coming back to school!

00:21:29.706 --> 00:21:32.625 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:21:37.088 --> 00:21:38.256 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
There you go!

00:21:38.340 --> 00:21:40.925 position:50% align:center
That's pretty much
how you use the Eggs.

00:21:41.009 --> 00:21:43.303 position:50% align:center
Huh? You don't seem
too enthusiastic.

00:21:43.386 --> 00:21:44.429 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
Hmm.

00:21:44.512 --> 00:21:46.431 position:50% align:center
You look as though
you don't trust us.

00:21:46.514 --> 00:21:47.557 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Really?

00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:49.851 position:50% align:center
After we broke it
down so neatly?

00:21:49.934 --> 00:21:52.729 position:50% align:center
That's not fair.

00:21:52.812 --> 00:21:54.314 position:50% align:center
We protect people.

00:21:54.397 --> 00:21:56.858 position:50% align:center
From dumb monsters.

00:21:56.941 --> 00:21:59.569 position:50% align:center
[MANTIS] This is a women's-only
car, you sneaky rat!

00:21:59.652 --> 00:22:02.697 position:50% align:center
I can be here
because I'm a girl!

00:22:02.781 --> 00:22:04.908 position:50% align:center
Get lost, hag!

00:22:06.659 --> 00:22:07.869 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Man.

00:22:07.952 --> 00:22:09.954 position:50% align:center
I'm just so tired.

00:22:10.038 --> 00:22:12.207 position:50% align:center
Make it go away.

00:22:15.835 --> 00:22:17.837 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Mannen.

00:22:17.921 --> 00:22:21.549 position:50% align:center
You have to keep your mom safe.

00:22:21.633 --> 00:22:22.634 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
All right.

00:22:22.717 --> 00:22:24.886 position:50% align:center
Next, we'll tell
you about ourselves.

00:22:24.969 --> 00:22:27.681 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Info about us'll cost you.

00:22:27.764 --> 00:22:29.933 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
However, that's all for today.

00:22:30.016 --> 00:22:34.646 position:50% align:center
But please drop in again
if you would like to hear more.

00:22:34.729 --> 00:22:35.855 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
We'll be waiting.

00:22:35.939 --> 00:22:39.609 position:50% align:center
Mannen. Let's go!

00:22:39.693 --> 00:22:45.240 position:50% align:center
I'll knock you off your
feet--with a shot to the heart!

00:22:50.078 --> 00:22:55.125 position:50% align:center
Hey. If I save more people,
then, will Koito come back?

00:22:55.208 --> 00:22:58.044 position:50% align:center
Tell me she will!

00:22:58.128 --> 00:23:00.171 position:50% align:center
[ACCA, URA-ACCA]
To be continued.